msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Vihāravagga "
msgstr "2. Meditation "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Dutiyauppādasutta "
msgstr "15. Arising (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.15, sc1
msgctxt "sn45.15:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.15:1.2"
msgid "“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā anuppannā uppajjanti, nāññatra sugatavinayā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these eight things don’t arise to be developed and cultivated apart from the Holy One’s training. "

msgctxt "sn45.15:1.3"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "sn45.15:1.4"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "They are: right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "sn45.15:1.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā anuppannā uppajjanti, nāññatra sugatavinayā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the eight things that don’t arise to be developed and cultivated apart from the Holy One’s training.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.15:1.6"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

